# Formulae

## Development Tools

brew "chezmoi" # Manage your dotfiles across multiple diverse machines, securely
brew "gh" # GitHub command-line tool
brew "git" # Distributed revision control system
brew "git-lfs" # Git extension for versioning large files
brew "gnupg" # GNU Pretty Good Privacy (PGP) package
brew "hashicorp/tap/terraform", trusted: true # Tool to build, change, and version infrastructure
brew "latexindent" # Add indentation to LaTeX files
brew "markdownlint-cli" # CLI for Node.js style checker and lint tool for Markdown files
brew "nodenv" # Manage multiple NodeJS versions
# Per https://github.com/nodenv/nodenv/issues/183, this seems like the best way to setup global packages
brew "nodenv/nodenv/nodenv-default-packages", trusted: true # Auto-installs packages for Node installs
brew "nodenv/nodenv/nodenv-nvmrc", trusted: true # Pick a node version from .nvmrc
brew "oci-cli" # Oracle Cloud Infrastructure CLI
brew "pinentry-mac" if OS.mac? # Pinentry for GPG on Mac
brew "pyenv" # Python version management
brew "shfmt" # Autoformat shell script source code
brew "tree" # Display directories as trees (with optional color/HTML output)
brew "yamllint" # Linter for YAML files
brew "zsh-completions" # Additional completion definitions for zsh

